column10: dig_threshold_desc:I aimed for around 20. Anything below 30 and I probably would leave unless the count had been going down slowly
column11: in which case I might go for another dig.
column17: other_desc:If the count was going down slowly I would be more likely to stay than on a planet where the count dropped quickly.
column18: feedback:It was a little glitchy. One or two times I got a \not in time\ message when I had pressed a button.}
